CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 28, 1945, pg. 3 reads: "Club Leader - Mrs. Abraham Lincoln, for her work with the Harriet Tubman Guild, the Federation of Women's Clubs, and other groups, was awarded one of the five citations. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Mrs. Abraham Lincoln holding bouquet at Business and Professional Association's banquet in Centre Avenue YMCA
